Name: facioscapulohumeral muscular dystrophy 1
Definition: A facioscapulohumeral muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in contraction of the D4Z4 macrosatellite repeat in the subtelomeric region of chromosome 4q35.

Name: facioscapulohumeral muscular dystrophy 2
Definition: A facioscapulohumeral muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in digenic inheritance of a heterozygous mutation in SMCHDI on 18p11.32 and a haplotype on chromosome 4 that is permissive for DUX4 expression.
